headline.print_headline: Barca's Luis Suarez Endorsed by Club Legend Luis Suarez
headline.main: Barca's Luis Suarez Endorsed by Club Legend Luis Suarez

lead_paragraph: Barcelona's Uruguay forward Luis Suarez has been given a ringing endorsement by one of the Catalan club's legendary players following his debut Barca goal on Tuesday -- his namesake Luis Suarez.
